Class MediaObject

java.lang.Object
org.gbif.api.model.common.MediaObject
Direct Known Subclasses:
NameUsageMediaObject
public class MediaObject extends Object
Metadata for a multimedia object representing an image, video or audio file. Based on DublinCore and the Simple Multimedia dwc archive extension:
